en-US.summary: See what you know about weird names of animals found on the internet.
en-US.name: quiz day
en-US.description:
Test your knowledge of weird internet animal names.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch quiz day" or "Alexa, open quiz day" to start the game.

At anytime, you can stop the game by saying "Alexa, stop"
